                      <desc>
                        Navigation system:
                        orange string is sewn into the fore edge or upper edge of <locus target="#1 #127 #130 #143"/>; green yarn is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#27"/>; white yarn is sewn into the upper edge of <locus target="#114"/>
                      </desc>
                      </item>
